rComments: This class is a math heavy engineering course, and not everything seemed ti be properly explained in class making learning difficult. You won't be told to but you need to read the manual to keep up with the pace of the class since not everything you are tested on is necessairly covered during lectures.

This class was a difficult class as it was seeing as it was switched from a third year class to a second year class. The fact that nothing seemed properly explained in class made the lectures and material difficult to understand. You must read the entire textbook to get a good understanding of the class material, you cannot just count on the slides

That prof is very nice and while her assignments are sometimes too hard, her exams are very fair, which is the way it should be and not the other way round. I just wish she wouldn't give a long assignment due on the week finals start, which really messed up the studying for process control. Apart from that, she really cares for her students.
An extremely helpful prof. with a very nice personality Very clear, cares for how her students do and the exams are no surprise
